    "image_with_text_AeCeAG": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_qWzGnX": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "About Revela",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_kNaVbD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Revela was created by a mother and her daughters, inspired by countless conversations with women who all shared the same frustration: sleepwear retailers simply aren’t meeting women’s needs.</p><p>We were tired of choosing between sleepwear that felt overly sexy, childish, synthetic, or poorly made. We wanted something elegant, comfortable, and thoughtfully crafted, sleepwear that respects how women actually live and rest.</p><p>The turning point came during an unexpected hospital stay, when finding appropriate sleepwear became a full-day expedition, ending empty-handed. Later, during menopause, breathable natural fabrics became essential rather than optional. Comfort, quality, and elegance were no longer preferences, they were non-negotiable.</p><h3>Sleepwear with meaning</h3><p>When the first Revela prototype was made, the feeling was immediate. It felt beautiful to wear. Comfortable. Considered.</p><p>For the first time, going to bed felt like an act of self-respect. Not for anyone else, but for yourself. This became the heart of our <em>Reveal You</em> philosophy.</p><p>Women tell us they feel beautiful wearing Revela. They sleep better. They feel more at ease. In busy lives filled with responsibility, choosing sleepwear that supports rest and wellbeing is not indulgent, it’s essential.</p><h3>Made with intention</h3><p>Every Revela piece is handcrafted by skilled South African women, using natural fibres chosen for their breathability, softness, and longevity. We create in small quantities, with care in every seam, because how something is made matters.</p><p><strong>Revela is more than sleepwear.</strong><br/><br/>It’s a quiet commitment to feeling good, every night.</p><p></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_Ltwy6V": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Get in touch",
            "button_link": "shopify://pages/contact",
            "button_style_secondary": true
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_qWzGnX",
