    "image_with_text_kbw7hE": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_f8ya4H": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why our fabrics matter",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_CWxjhp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Revela, fabric is never an afterthought, it defines how each garment feels, moves, and lasts.</p><p>We work primarily with premium Liberty Tana Lawn® cotton, an ultra-fine cotton fabric printed in Italy and celebrated worldwide for its silky softness, breathability, and exceptional quality. Lightweight yet durable, it feels cool against the skin, drapes beautifully, and becomes even softer with wear.</p><p>Chosen for both comfort and beauty, our fabrics are gentle on sensitive skin, easy to care for, and designed to retain their elegance wash after wash.</p><p>Every print is carefully selected to celebrate individuality and femininity, while each garment is handcrafted in small batches by skilled South African women.</p><p>The result is sleepwear that combines luxury, comfort, and craftsmanship, without compromise.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
